This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3890

This is a dark 256 color scheme with mild contrast and not so many colors. It is good for prolonged coding. This scheme is inspaired by Lucius (vimscript #2536).

Please use the Github repo, where the script will be updated: https://github.com/zefei/simple-dark

